    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I have added support for aggregate sequences in one of my development branches.\nIt requires more boilerplate than your example yaml, but it is more general (see e.g. #6631):\n\n``` yaml\nhtnk:\n    idle:\n        Combine:\n            htnk01:\n            htnk02:\n            ...\n            htnk31:\n            htnk32:\n        Facings: 32\n    turret:\n        Combine:\n            htnk33:\n            htnk34:\n            ...\n            htnk63:\n            htnk64:\n        Facings: 32\n```\n"
